The Smoke Tests errand runs basic functionality tests against your Elastic Runtime deployment after an installation or update. In this section, choose where to run smoke tests. In the **Errands** section, you can choose whether or not to run the Smoke Tests errand. 

1. Select **Smoke Tests**. 

1. If you have a shared apps domain, select **Temporary org and space**, which creates an ad-hoc org and space for running smoke tests and deletes them afterwards. Otherwise, select **Specified org and space** and complete the fields to specify where you want to run smoke tests.  

	<%= image_tag('smoke-test-er-config.png') %>

1. Click **Save**.